    • getSessionFactory

      public SessionFactoryImplementor getSessionFactory()
      Description copied from interface: SqlAstCreationContext
      Avoid calling this method directly, as much as possible. SQL AST creation should not depend on the existence of a session factory, so if you need to obtain this object, there's something wrong with the design.

      Currently this is only called when creating a TableGroup, but we will introduce a new sort of creation context for that, probably.

      Specified by:
